                                <li><strong>Location in School:</strong> <i>@schoolLocation</i><br /></li>
                                <li><strong>Hours of Operation:</strong> <i>@schoolHours</i></li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>With more than 20 <a href="https://www.applefcu.org/AppleWeb/Locations" target="_blank">branches</a> across Northern Virginia, <a href="https://www.applefcu.org/personal-banking/digital-services" target="_blank">FREE Online Banking</a>, <a href="https://www.applefcu.org/personal-banking/digital-services" target="_blank">FREE Mobile Apps</a>*, as well as access to more than 53,000 Surcharge-FREE** ATMs nationwide, no matter where you go, we’re nearby.</p>
